252
00:15:52,110 --> 00:15:53,910
Ah, mati aku.

253
00:15:56,130 --> 00:16:00,010
Insting Asta langsung memahaminya.

254
00:16:00,010 --> 00:16:05,130
Asta selama ini selalu gunakan
